<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Velmira</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
            background-color: #f9f7f8;
        }
        
        a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .email-header {
            background-color: #e9dfe5;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #5e3d4d;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 120px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fdfdfd;
        }
        
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #e9dfe5;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #5e3d4d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 280px;
            width: 70%;
            min-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        /* Mobile responsiveness */
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                padding: 10px;
                margin: 10px;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                min-height: 100px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                max-width: 250px;
                width: 80%;
                min-width: 180px;
            }
            
            .email-body {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            body {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
        
        /* Large screens */
        @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            .email-header {
                padding: 50px 30px;
                min-height: 140px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                max-width: 320px;
                width: 60%;
            }
        }
        
        /* Extra small screens */
        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                padding: 5px;
                margin: 5px;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 25px 15px;
                min-height: 80px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                max-width: 200px;
                width: 85%;
                min-width: 150px;
            }
            
            .email-body {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            body {
                font-size: 13px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="cid:logo" alt="Velmira Logo" class="logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello
                <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>Velmira</strong>, where velvet meets mirror and your skin becomes its truest reflection.</p>
            <p>We're here to guide you toward radiant, confident skin with gentle, science-led care. Start with our personalized Skin Analysis tool and explore products designed to match your unique glow.</p>
            <p>Thanks for being here. Let's glow together.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy;2025 Velmira. Reflect Your Radiance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>